{
  "stem": "1208.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'd eat with us, and he'd send them off with some money or shirts that they needed or jackets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a giving atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "School was a small Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In retrospect, I can see that we learned so much in this little school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our teacher exposed us not only to secular studies, but in the afternoon, we had Hebrew and Yiddish, and all that went with it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when it came time for me to go to high school, I couldn't go already.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only my oldest sister could go to the lyceum.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my parents later sent me to a school in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I made my abitur privately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went to Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Frenkel's kindergarten seminar in Berlin, in Grunewald.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lived on our block.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came to us for Passover and Hanukkah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would go to their house for Easter and Weihnachten.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were told we couldn't eat the meal, just the sweets we could have.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we played together until Hitler came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then it all changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember one incident when my brother's friend stood across the street and said to him, we can't play with you anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Wolfgang said, why not, you're my best friend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, no, my father is in the SR now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, you're Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're going to take your house away soon because we like your house better than ours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from then on, they would throw stones at us and ostracize us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was hazardous to even walk to school or take our bicycles to school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were often assaulted by people who had been our friends before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I must have been 12, 13.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The incident with these children on our block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the first.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
